thread.title: Frank Petrini
thread.title_full: Totally Wicked E-liquid USA inc. reviewed by Frank Petrini

author: Frank Petrini
title: Frank Petrini
text: I've been treated well and am very happy with ToTally Wicked E-Liquid USA inc. for all my e-cigarette needs. Sometimes I think their prices might be a little high but they have enough sales promotions that I believe make their products reasonable. When they have a promotion I usually stock up on the items I use the most.
